verbose_text: Further, it may be easier for well functioning families to adapt to the demands of sDOR, which requires some level of already established routines and overall healthy family dynamics.33 To help families effectively adapt to sDOR, Brenner FIT provides family therapy from licensed counselors trained in motivational interviewing,34 thus it is important for providers to keep this in mind when adopting a similar treatment approach.
